summary: An ordinance quit-claiming to John Marshall Maggs, a bachelor, and Molly Maggs Fisher, formerly Molly Maggs, all right, title and interest of the City of Seattle in and to Lot 7, Block 1, Union Lake Supplemental Addition, by reason of the filing of an indemnity agreement (Auditor's File No. 1705572) covering the construction and maintenance of a certain retaining wall.
